{
  "id": "connect-anydocs-mcp",
  "lang": "zh",
  "slug": "connect-anydocs-mcp",
  "title": "把 Anydocs MCP 接入 Codex",
  "description": "让 Codex 能够安全地读取和写入 Anydocs 项目。",
  "tags": [
    "mcp",
    "setup"
  ],
  "status": "published",
  "updatedAt": "2026-04-02T00:00:00.000Z",
  "content": {
    "version": 1,
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-1",
        "level": 1,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "把 Anydocs MCP 接入 Codex"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "典型配置思路："
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "id": "block-3",
        "style": "numbered",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "element-3-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "在 Codex 中注册 `@anydocs/mcp` 为一个 `stdio` MCP server"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-4-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "让 Codex 在进入项目时读取项目根目录里的最小化 `AGENTS.md`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-5-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "把 `anydocs://authoring/guidance` 当成详细工作流说明的来源"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-6",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "推荐默认顺序是："
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "id": "block-7",
        "style": "bulleted",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "element-7-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "`project_open`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-8-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "查看 `project_open.authoring.templates`、`resources`、`resourceTemplates`；模板选择不确定时用 `page_template_query`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-9-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "如果页面会用到 `template` / `metadata`，先确认对应 template 的 `metadataSchema`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-10-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "需要详细 guidance 或 canonical 示例时，再读取 `anydocs://authoring/guidance`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-11-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "`page_list` / `page_find` / `page_get`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-12-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "如果要新增或更新模板定义，先用 `page_template_save`；然后用 `page_create_from_template` 或 `page_create`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-13-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "`page_update` / `page_set_status`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-14-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "`nav_get` / `nav_insert` / `nav_delete` / `nav_move`"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-15",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "这样做的好处是："
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "id": "block-16",
        "style": "bulleted",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "element-16-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "页面写入会经过 Anydocs 的 domain validation"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-17-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "template metadata 会遵守 schema 约束"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-18-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "页面发布仍然遵守发布审批规则"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-19-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "agent 行为更稳定，也更容易复现"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
